下載並安裝 python
https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-387/

完成後, 右鍵點選 get-pip,  點選 Edit with IDLE -> Edit with IDLE 3.8
開啟程式後, 點選上排 Run -> Run Module, 安裝 pip

安裝完成後, 開啟 cmd 
cd C:\Users\xxxxxxx\AppData\Local\Programs\Python\Python38\Scripts
安裝相關套件
easy_install beautifulsoup4
easy_install selenium
easy_install webdriver-manager

下載 webchrome driver
https://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html?path=94.0.4606.61/

注意, webchrome driver 需與程式放在同一個資料夾

完成後, 右鍵點選 demo,  點選 Edit with IDLE -> Edit with IDLE 3.8
開啟程式後, 點選上排 Run -> Run Module, 執行程式
